Package: ccfdata
Type: Package
Title: R Client for the Canadian Climate Framing Data API
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Antoine", "Lemorphic", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "antoine.lemor@usherbrooke.ca"),
    person("Tristan", "Boursier", role = "aut",
           email = "tristan.boursier@sciencespo.fr"))
Description: Authenticated client for the Canadian Climate Framing (CCF)
    data platform at <https://data.ccf-project.ca>. Wraps the CCF HTTP API
    in tibble-friendly helpers for searching the 250,000-article climate
    coverage corpus (1978-2024), inspecting the 67-category annotation
    framework, and exploring cross-year media cascades and event clusters.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/antoinelemor/r-ccf-data, https://ccf-project.ca
